#: docs/admin/25.domains/certificate.mdx:1
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Certificate"
msgstr "Certificado"

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/25.domains/certificate.mdx:9
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Certificates are used to guarantee the confidentiality and authenticity of the communication between a web browser and your server. In particular, they protect against attackers trying to impersonate your server.\n"
msgstr "Los certificados sirven para garantizar la confidencialidad y la autenticidad de las comunicaciones entre un navegador web y tu servidor. En particular, permite proteger los visitantes contra atacantes que podrían intentar de robar la identidad del servidor.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/25.domains/certificate.mdx:11
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "YunoHost provides a **self-signed** certificate, it means that your server guaranties the certificate validity. It's enough **for personal usage**, because you trust your own server. But this could be a problem if you want to open access to anonymous like web user for a website.\n"
msgstr "Por defecto, YunoHost provee un certificado **auto-firmado**, lo que significa que es tu servidor el que garantiza la validez del certificado. Es suficiente **en el caso de un uso personal**, porque puedes confiar en tu propio servidor, pero esto planteará problemas si piensas en abrir el acceso a tu servidor a personas anónimas, por ejemplo si quieres alojar un sitio web.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/25.domains/certificate.mdx:13
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "In practice, visitors will see a screen list this:\n"
msgstr "En efecto, los usuarios deberán pasar por una pantalla de este tipo :\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/25.domains/certificate.mdx:17
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Which basically asks the visitor : **\"Do you trust the server hosting this website?\"**. This can rightfully frighten a lot of people.\n"
msgstr "Esta pantalla equivale a que te pidan ** ¿ Confías en el servidor que aloja este sitio ? ***. Esto puede asustar tu usuarios (con toda la razón).\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/25.domains/certificate.mdx:19
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "To avoid this confusion, it's possible to get a certificate signed a known authority named **Let's Encrypt** which provide free certificates directly recognized by browsers. YunoHost allows to directly install this certificate from the web administration interface or from the command line.\n"
msgstr "To avoid this confusion, it's possible to get a certificate signed a known authority named **Let's Encrypt** which provide free certificates directly recognized by browsers. YunoHost allows to directly install this certificate from the web administration interface or from the command line.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: docs/admin/25.domains/certificate.mdx:20
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Install a Let's Encrypt certificate"
msgstr "Instalar un certificado Let's Encrypt"

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/25.domains/certificate.mdx:23
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Before attempting to install a Let's Encrypt certificate, you should make sure that your DNS is correctly configured (your.domain.tld should point to your server's IP) and that your domain is accessible through HTTP from outside your local network (i.e. at least port 80 should be forwarded to your server).\n"
msgstr "Antes de intentar la instalación de un certificado Let's Encrypt, primero debes asegurarte de que el DNS está configurado correctamente (tu.dominio.tld debe apuntar hacia la IP de tu servidor) y que el sitio está accesible en HTTP desde afuera (i.e. por lo menos que el puerto 80 está correctamente redirigido hacia tu servidor).\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/25.domains/certificate.mdx:28
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Go to the 'Domain' part of the admin interface, then in the section dedicated to your.domain.tld. You should find a 'SSL certificate' button:\n"
msgstr "En la categoría 'Dominio' de la interfaz de administración, y luego en la sección dedicada a tu dominio, encontrarás un botón 'Certificado SSL'.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/25.domains/certificate.mdx:32
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "In the 'SSL certificate' section, you can see the status of the current certificate. If you just added the domain, it should be a self-signed certificate.\n"
msgstr ""
"En la sección 'Certificado SSL', puedes ver el estado corriente del certificado.\n"
"Si acabas de añadir el dominio, ya dispone de un certificado auto-firmado.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/25.domains/certificate.mdx:36
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "If your domain is correctly configured, it is then possible to install the Let's Encrypt certificate via the green button.\n"
msgstr "Si tu dominio está configurado correctamente, es posible instalar un certificado Let's Encrypt vía el botón verde.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/25.domains/certificate.mdx:40
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Once the install is made, you can check that the certificate is live via your browser by going to your domain in HTTPS. The certificate will automatically be renewed every three months.\n"
msgstr "Una vez la instalación terminada, puedes ir a tu dominio vía tu navegador, en HTTPS, para comprobar que tu certificado está bien firmado por Let's Encrypt. El certificado se renovará automáticamente al cabo de cada periodo de tres meses.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/25.domains/certificate.mdx:47
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
